    title: 'Handles Building Photo Messages',
    text: "Developers and property owners message with photos of buildings they want demolished — 'what would it cost to clear this site?' The AI asks about the frame type, floor area, asbestos status, and programme, converting a casual photo into a tender-ready demolition brief."
  },
  {
    icon: '⚡',
    title: 'Captures Neighbourhood Clearance Enquiries',
    text: "When you demolish a prominent local building, neighbours and adjacent property owners become aware of demolition services. They message: 'you just demolished the old factory — can you quote for our derelict outbuilding?' The AI converts proximity interest into domestic leads."
  },
  {
    icon: '🕐',
