    title: 'Qualifies Casual Demolition Enquiries',
    text: "Messenger conversations about demolition start loose — 'how much to knock down a garage?' The AI asks about construction material, roof type, base, services, and access — producing a quotable domestic demolition brief."
  },
  {
    icon: '🔗',
    title: 'Monetises Dramatic Content',
