<ChannelTradeLayout
  title="AI Facebook Messenger for UK Demolition Contractors | Rapid Receptionist"
  description={`AI Facebook Messenger for UK demolition contractors. Converts high-reach takedown videos and site clearance showcases into developer tenders. Add-on at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month.`}
  canonicalUrl="/demolition-contractors/ai-facebook-messenger/"
  channelName="AI Facebook Messenger"
  tradeName="Demolition Contractor"
  tradeNamePlural="Demolition Contractors"
  tradeSlug="demolition-contractors"
  headline="AI Facebook Messenger for UK Demolition Contractor Companies"
  accentWord="Demolition"
  subhead="You post a timelapse of a controlled soft-strip on a Victorian warehouse. A developer messages about demolishing a derelict pub for flats. Your AI captures the brief while you load a grab lorry."
  scenario="It is 10pm on a Wednesday. A farmer near Charlbury has three derelict agricultural buildings — a former dairy with a collapsing corrugated asbestos cement roof, a Dutch barn with a rusting steel frame, and a concrete block silage clamp that has not been used in twenty years. The farm wants the structures demolished and the area cleared for a new agricultural storage building under permitted development. He finds your Facebook page through a Cotswold farming group and messages: 'Hello — got 3 old farm buildings that need taking down. An old dairy with a dodgy roof (might be asbestos), a Dutch barn with a steel frame, and a concrete silage clamp. All derelict. We want the area cleared for a new agricultural building. Can you handle all 3? Rural access but we can get a lorry down the track. Charlbury area.' Without AI Messenger, you see the message Thursday morning. One competitor replied at 10:30pm with a helpful rural demolition explanation. With AI Messenger, the reply arrives at 10:01pm: 'Thank you — we handle agricultural demolition regularly. The dairy roof will need testing for asbestos before demolition. Could you confirm the approximate sizes of each building and whether you want the concrete bases broken out or left in place? We will plan the sequence around the asbestos removal.' He provides approximate dimensions. Thursday you open the lead and call at 8am."
  benefits={benefits}
  faqs={faqs}
  channelPageUrl="/construction-trades/ai-facebook-messenger/"
  tradePageUrl="/demolition-contractors/ai-receptionist/"
  ctaHeadline="Turn High-Reach Drone Footage into Care Home Demolition Tenders"
  ctaSubhead={`A drone reel earns two hundred and forty likes. AI Messenger converts every property investor message into a demolition tender with floor area, ACM status, and development timeline. Add-on at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month.`}
/>
